  <h1 class="case-study">MYOB Time Tracking for AccountRight</h1>
  <img src="/images/preview-images.png" alt="Preview of the app" />
  <p>The following case study describes the process my team and I took to develop this app for iOS and Android. The app enabled MYOB customers who bill for their time to capture their activities on the phone rather than requiring the use of our desktop software to enter in their software.</p>
  <p>I was the sole Product Designer working together with a team comprising of a Product Manager, Business Analyst and Developers to ship the product. We worked very tightly together in iterative cycles with a focus on delivering working software at the end of each round. In addition to the development team, I developed a close relationship with our customers through the process by asking for feedback consistently. </p>
