  '<p>As this was to be a companion app to the MYOB desktop product. The first part of discovery was understanding the part of the desktop product we were affecting. Since the goal was to get something out fast, this involved me mapping out the steps required to submit an activity slip on the desktop.</p>
  <p>I also had conversations with our Product Manager as well as other stakeholders within the company to better understand the target audience, and the reasons they used the product.</p>',
