  '<video width="100%" loop autoplay controls><source src="/images/framer-prototype.mp4"></video>
  <p class="caption">Fig 2 - Framer Prototype</p>',
  '<p>Based on this information, I first started with an extremely rough prototype to map out how we could translate the desktop process into a mobile one. I built out the flow using Framer and had an interactive prototype to generate discussion. I then used the prototype to spark conversations with our developers to understand what was possible, and what was not. The prototype included lots of nods to features that I wanted to understand could be possible.</p>'
