  '<p>In order to aid mobile development of other apps within MYOB, designers at MYOB worked together to establish a common mobile design style guide to be used across different MYOB mobile apps. After we agreed on a common style guide, we started to roll it out across the time tracking app which made it look a lot better and more modern.</p>
  <p>We also added a timer function to the app, which was one of the most requested features to the app. In addition to this, we included many small bug fixes and workflow issues that were included as part of the feedback.</p>',
